Resource Profile: ProfileObservationDefinition

0.0.1-snapshot-3
Official URL: http://hl7.org/fhir/5.0/StructureDefinition/profile-ObservationDefinition Version:
Standards status: Trial-use Active as of 2026-02-09 Maturity Level: 0 Computable Name: ProfileObservationDefinition

This cross-version profile allows R5 ObservationDefinition content to be represented via FHIR R4 ObservationDefinition resources.

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: Cross-version Extension `R5.ClinicalUseDefinition` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.NutritionIntake` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.Observation.instantiates[x]` for use in FHIR R4, Cross-version Extension `R5.PlanDefinition.action` for use in FHIR R4... Show 2 more, Cross-version Extension `R5.RequestOrchestration.action.definition[x]` for use in FHIR R4 and Cross-version Extension `R5.RequestOrchestration.action` for use in FHIR R4

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
